  "detailed_description": "Flying cats versus 10,000 soothing characters!<br>What awaits them beyond all those furious midair fights...?<br>Witness the world's most shocking ending for yourself!<br><br>Shoot, evade, and detonate Bombers!<br>Neko Navy is an exhilarating horizontal-scrolling shooter with easy controls.<br><br>The game offers three difficulties that everyone from a beginner to an advanced player can enjoy.<br>Fire off as many Bombers as you can to achieve high scores!<br><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Horizontal single-player shoot'em'up <br></li><li>7 Stages<br></li><li>3 Difficulties (EASY, HARD, DEATH)<br></li><li>6 Playable cats(?)<br></li><li>Soundtrack included</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Flying cats versus 10,000 soothing characters!<br>What awaits them beyond all those furious midair fights...?<br>Witness the world's most shocking ending for yourself!<br><br>Shoot, evade, and detonate Bombers!<br>Neko Navy is an exhilarating horizontal-scrolling shooter with easy controls.<br><br>The game offers three difficulties that everyone from a beginner to an advanced player can enjoy.<br>Fire off as many Bombers as you can to achieve high scores!<br><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Horizontal single-player shoot'em'up <br></li><li>7 Stages<br></li><li>3 Difficulties (EASY, HARD, DEATH)<br></li><li>6 Playable cats(?)<br></li><li>Soundtrack included</li></ul>",
